158
00:13:02,774 --> 00:13:04,243
Ini satu-satunya salinan.

159
00:13:04,244 --> 00:13:05,503
<i>Bahkan jika tidak terlibat pun.</i>

160
00:13:05,504 --> 00:13:07,842
